org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.vendorextension.v6extension

Class V6Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.OFMatch
      • org.opendaylight.controller.protocol_plugin.openflow.vendorextension.v6extension.V6Match
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class V6Match
extends org.openflow.protocol.OFMatch
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    This Class forms the vendor specific IPv6 Flow Match messages as well as processes the vendor specific IPv6 Stats Reply message. For message creation, it parses the user entered IPv6 match fields, creates a sub-message for each field which are later used to form the complete message. For message processing, it parses the incoming message and reads each field of the message and stores in appropriate field of V6Match object.
